@0    = ~You are new to Arlax? In that case you are most welcome. We have three good inns here. All in perfect shape. Be sure to pay them all a visit.~
@1    = ~There is also a Temple of Helm here. If you are in a need of healing it is the right place to go.~
@2    = ~We also have a great smith here. You can find him next to the temple. I think you really should have a conversation with him.~
@3    = ~You should go and talk with the smith. He can forge amazing things.~
